&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;There is no change of oxidation numbers, and thus it is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;not a redox reaction&lt;/span&gt;. It is an example of a&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Double decomposition reaction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;For the reaction:&lt;strong&gt; 2KCIO&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 2KCI + 3O&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

