&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Here,&lt;strong&gt; Cl &lt;/strong&gt;is getting from oxidation state +5 to -1, i.e., the oxidation number decreases and it is&lt;strong&gt; reduced.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Oxygen&lt;/strong&gt; is getting &lt;strong&gt;oxidised&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is an example of&amp;nbsp;a&lt;strong&gt; redox reaction &lt;/strong&gt;as both oxidation and reduction take place.&lt;/p&gt;

