	&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The species Br and Cl are oxidized and reduced respectively. Hence it is an example of&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;a redox reaction.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;I&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 2S&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;O&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;-2&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr;&amp;nbsp; 2I&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;+S&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;O&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;-2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

